text: No one wants to talk about this but above a certain iq you can basically change your iq to whatever you want within +3sd. Eg a 145 can become a 155 after a year of intense focus (a 95 could not go to 105, and even worse, 10pts around the middle is less useful)
yes they can, and they can actually become that much smarter, too

it’s a thick chunk of the curve. Exercise and meditation doesn’t get you ahead of ~25% of people ahead of you — but you’re right that 100s could test as anywhere between 90 and 110 based on present mental clarity
many cases of smart people bootstrapping techniques to increase the speed, clarity, and recall of their mind. Overall effect is increase in raw G
this is where “I’ll be frank with you originates”—bypassing social cues and saying directly the matter at hand
